298
00:24:30,457 --> 00:24:34,497
Mrs Sherli and Mrs Vijay Malhotra...

299
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:41,499
But Amna and Sunanda...

300
00:24:41,499 --> 00:24:45,528
May be able to pour their hearts out to each other...

301
00:24:47,609 --> 00:24:49,622
That's right...

302
00:24:50,338 --> 00:24:52,091
Suninda...

303
00:24:52,440 --> 00:24:54,220
Sunanda...

304
00:24:54,340 --> 00:24:56,682
Sunenda...

305
00:24:59,089 --> 00:25:03,749
Don't worry too much about Nadir, okay?

306
00:25:03,790 --> 00:25:07,290
